title Aegis Deployment Architecture on Azure

direction down

// A) Source and Build
Source and Build [icon: git-branch, color: gray] {
  GitHub Repository [icon: github]
  GitHub Actions [icon: github-actions]

  Build Jobs [icon: package] {
    Frontend Build [icon: react, label: "Frontend Build"]
    Backend Build [icon: docker, label: "Backend Image"]
    Test Suite [icon: check-circle, label: "Tests"]
  }
}

Azure Container Registry [icon: azure-container-registries]

// B) Deployment Targets
Environments [icon: azure-subscriptions] {
  Dev [color: gray, icon: code] {
    Dev Front Door [icon: azure-front-door-and-cdn-profiles, label: "Front Door"]
    Dev Frontend App [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Frontend"]
    Dev Backend API [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Backend API"]
  }

  Staging [color: yellow, icon: layers] {
    Staging Front Door [icon: azure-front-door-and-cdn-profiles, label: "Front Door"]
    Staging Frontend App [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Frontend"]
    Staging Backend API [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Backend API"]
  }

  Prod [color: green, icon: shield] {
    Prod Front Door [icon: azure-front-door-and-cdn-profiles, label: "Front Door"]
    Prod Frontend App [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Frontend"]
    Prod Backend API [icon: azure-container-apps, label: "Backend API"]
    Previous Image Tag [icon: archive, label: "Previous Release"]
  }
}

// C) Runtime Dependencies
Runtime Services [icon: azure-resource-groups, color: blue] {
  Azure OpenAI [icon: azure-openai]
  Azure AI Search [icon: azure-cognitive-search]
  Azure Maps [icon: azure-maps-accounts]
  Operational Database [icon: azure-cosmos-db]
  Key Vault [icon: azure-key-vault]
}

// D) Operations
Operations [icon: azure-monitor, color: purple] {
  Azure Monitor [icon: azure-monitor]
  Application Insights [icon: azure-application-insights]
  Alerts [icon: bell]
  Ops Channel [icon: message-circle, label: "On-call / Ops"]
}

// Source and Build Connections
GitHub Repository > GitHub Actions: commit/push
GitHub Actions > Build Jobs: build & test
Frontend Build > Azure Container Registry: publish image
Backend Build > Azure Container Registry: publish image
Test Suite > Azure Container Registry

// Deployment Connections
Azure Container Registry > Dev Frontend App: deploy release
Azure Container Registry > Dev Backend API: deploy release
Azure Container Registry > Staging Frontend App: deploy release
Azure Container Registry > Staging Backend API: deploy release
Azure Container Registry > Prod Frontend App: deploy release
Azure Container Registry > Prod Backend API: deploy release

// Rollback Path
Previous Image Tag > Prod Backend API: rollback
Previous Image Tag > Prod Frontend App: rollback
Prod Backend API <-- Previous Image Tag: snapshot on deploy

// Public Traffic Flow
Dev Front Door > Dev Frontend App: public traffic
Dev Frontend App > Dev Backend API: service-to-service
Staging Front Door > Staging Frontend App: public traffic
Staging Frontend App > Staging Backend API: service-to-service
Prod Front Door > Prod Frontend App: public traffic
Prod Frontend App > Prod Backend API: service-to-service

// Runtime Dependencies
Dev Backend API > Azure OpenAI: service-to-service
Dev Backend API > Azure AI Search: service-to-service
Dev Backend API > Azure Maps: service-to-service
Dev Backend API > Operational Database: service-to-service
Dev Backend API > Key Vault: secret retrieval

Staging Backend API > Azure OpenAI: service-to-service
Staging Backend API > Azure AI Search: service-to-service
Staging Backend API > Azure Maps: service-to-service
Staging Backend API > Operational Database: service-to-service
Staging Backend API > Key Vault: secret retrieval

Prod Backend API > Azure OpenAI: service-to-service
Prod Backend API > Azure AI Search: service-to-service
Prod Backend API > Azure Maps: service-to-service
Prod Backend API > Operational Database: service-to-service
Prod Backend API > Key Vault: secret retrieval

// Operations Telemetry
Dev Backend API --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Dev Frontend App --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Staging Backend API --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Staging Frontend App --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Prod Backend API --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Prod Frontend App --> Azure Monitor: telemetry & alerts
Azure OpenAI --> Application Insights: telemetry & alerts
Azure AI Search --> Application Insights: telemetry & alerts
Operational Database --> Application Insights: telemetry & alerts
Azure Monitor > Application Insights
Application Insights > Alerts: telemetry & alerts
Alerts > Ops Channel: telemetry & alerts

legend {
  [connection: ">", label: "Direct flow / deployment"]
  [connection: "-->", label: "Async telemetry / snapshot"]
  [color: gray, label: "Development environment"]
  [color: yellow, label: "Staging environment"]
  [color: green, label: "Production environment"]
}
